text: Maga jara tumhi tyacyavisayi sansayagrasta asala, je amhi tumacyakade pathavile ahe tara tumhi tya lokanna vicara je tumacya purvicya granthance pathana karatata. Nihsansaya tumacyajavala tumacya palanakartyatarphe satyanistha grantha ala ahe tevha tumhi kadhihi sanka karanaryampaiki ho'u naka
